      • isBundleEnabled

        public static boolean isBundleEnabled(java.lang.String bundleName)
        Determine whether the given bundle exists.

        Note this is just as much work as getting a string, so it should really only be called at most once per bundleName.

        Parameters:
        bundleName -
        Returns:
        true if there exists a ResourceBundle of the given name, false otherwise
